et. I was a very big sportsman then. Oh I've - used to play cricket - we used to be up there - on a field playing cricket - or football in the football season, and I joined - Burslem next door here football club, 1923, think it were. Mm. 1920 I played for
 Burslem {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname State}}Victoria{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, and - I won a signed up cup up there with them. And - the same time George Shankton was playing for the first team and he - he signed on with Port Vale, and become a professional with them.
