\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12386321 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6637546\charrsid4489010 
Well, when I was - from sixteen she allowed us to eleven o'clock. And we never abused that, we'd be generally in by just turned ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7806616 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6637546\charrsid4489010 Did you make any new friends at this time? You mentioned that you were 
