Well - yes, well we - we got host of friends because - the - the - there was nothing to beat these terraced type houses, for making friends. And - there'd be - a gang of us and we'd go - but we'd never - annoy anybo
dy, same as today. We treated the elders with respect as we should do, but - but today, I can't understand 'em. My contention is - they don't know, they've got that much money they don't know what to do. They're bored with life. Where - when we was young 
- we haven't got the money, we had to make our enjoyment, we found our happiness in finding that enjoyment.
\par 
